Three-Level Caching Stack. Level 1 (Prompt Cache/KV-Cache): Same Prompt Prefix -> Reuse KV-Cache -> Save 50-90% Prefill Time, 50% Input Cost. Providers: Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, vLLM. Level 2 (Response Cache): Exact Match -> SHA-256 Hash -> 100% Call Savings. Use: FAQ, Status Queries. Level 3 (Semantic Cache): Similar Query -> Embedding -> Vector Search -> Threshold 0.92 -> 20-40% Savings. Use: Support, Docs, Wikis. Clean stack diagram, German labels.